videos.description: Virginia Tech's Justin Robinson attacks the lane to lay it in.
videos.headline: Robinson flies past BC defense for the score

videos.description: Boston College's Jordan Chatman sets an ACC record for consecutive 3-pointers in a game.
videos.headline: Chatman three sets ACC record

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Justin Bibbs catches and fires just before the clock expires at the end of the first half.
videos.headline: Bibbs beats the first half buzzer with a long 3-pointer

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Seth Allen pump fakes, then springs to the rim to lay it in.
videos.headline: Allen's pump fake opens up the lane to score

videos.description: Off an inbounds pass, Virginia Tech swings it around the perimeter to Seth Allen who drains a three.
videos.headline: Good ball movement sets up an Allen 3-pointer.

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Justin Robinson goes to the rim past a couple defenders to lay it in.
videos.headline: Robinson skies to split two defenders and score

videos.description: Virginia Tech's Ty Outlaw sends a shot attempt flying out of bounds.
videos.headline: Outlaw denies a BC shot attempt
